wnload PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3616489\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3616489\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vfj1665703025321.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vfj1665703025321.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vfj1665703025321.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vfj1665703025321\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Modeled Component\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Modeled Component is a Component that can be used to create derived components, which inherit the component-level properties, code containers, and constants from the modeled component.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__p_d95387e1_d95388e1_d95389e1\">Modeled components are used to speed development and ensure\n      consistency between components with a similar purpose. A modeled component defines a pattern\n      for a specific type of component, including its structure, properties, and layout, and this\n      pattern is copied to components that are derived from it.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__section_iqy_dfn_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d181960e54\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">cpt</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yth1665702550544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yth1665702550544.html\" title=\"A Component Entity is a Development Object that represents data that is owned by a Component. It is part of the Component’s structure and is maintained as part of the Component, although it may reference and inherit from a Modeled Entity.\">Component Entity</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wyt1665702609153.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyt1665702609153.html\" title=\"A Label is a Development Object that contains text that appears on a presentation component. Labels have properties, but most cannot be set dynamically.\">Label</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>, Generic Entity,\n                  Generic Field</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"srw1665702550375.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/srw1665702550375.html\" title=\"A Main Development Object is a Development Object that has no parent object, is maintained using a dedicated editor, and can be saved and exported as a single unit, with all its children.\">Main Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Example URI:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vfj1665703025321__table_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">cpt:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ModeledComponentName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__section_vtt_ffn_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d181960e252\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__p_d95396e1_d95397e1_d95398e1\">Modeled Component specializes Main Development Object and\n        Component in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__ul_tmn_gfn_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37745e1_d37746e1_d37747e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__p_d95399e1_d95400e1_d95401e1\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Modeled Component</span> property\n            is <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>. This causes Uniface to automatically define compile-time\n            constants for any generic entities and fields.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37748e1_d37749e1_d37750e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__p_d95402e1_d95403e1_d95404e1\">It can contain generic entities and fields.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37751e1_d37752e1_d37753e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__p_d95405e1_d95406e1_d95407e1\">No runtime objects are generated.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__section_ugs_gfn_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d181960e288\">Properties</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__p_d95411e1_d95412e1_d95413e1\">Object Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__ul_mrd_3fn_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37754e1_d37755e1_d37756e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37757e1_d37758e1_d37759e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owq1665702585461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owq1665702585461.html\" title=\"Type of Development Object. Read only.\">Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37760e1_d37761e1_d37762e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybn1665702585544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybn1665702585544.html\" title=\"Complete URI of the Development Object. Read only.\">Location</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37763e1_d37764e1_d37765e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37766e1_d37767e1_d37768e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ipc1665702585697.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ipc1665702585697.html\" title=\"Use this property to provide comments or instructions for the selected development object. You can use the toolbar and standard Windows keyboard shortcuts to format the text, copy and paste, and undo and redo edits.\">Documentation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__p_d95414e1_d95415e1_d95416e1\">Source Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__ul_xrd_3fn_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37769e1_d37770e1_d37771e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cnn1665702762358.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cnn1665702762358.html\" title=\"Read-only property the records the date and time when the object was last modified. The value is set by Uniface.\">Date Modified</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__p_d95417e1_d95418e1_d95419e1\">Configuration Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__ul_yrd_3fn_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37772e1_d37773e1_d37774e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wyl1665702688770.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyl1665702688770.html\" title=\"Specifies the library containing the global objects used by the component or application shell. If no library is specified, the library defined for the application shell is used. Otherwise, SYSTEM_LIBRARY is used as the default.\">Library</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37775e1_d37776e1_d37777e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dfn1665702688838.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dfn1665702688838.html\" title=\"This property determines whether the component is a modeled component.\">Is Modeled Component</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37778e1_d37779e1_d37780e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mwa1665702688914.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mwa1665702688914.html\" title=\"This property specifies the name of the modeled component from which this component is derived.\">Modeled Component</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__p_d95420e1_d95421e1_d95422e1\">Behavior Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__ul_esd_3fn_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37781e1_d37782e1_d37783e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"obc1665703043525.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/obc1665703043525.html\" title=\"Specifies the type of Uniface Component.\">Component Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37784e1_d37785e1_d37786e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qsg1665702688984.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qsg1665702688984.html\" title=\"Determines the degree to which data in the component can be edited and stored.\">Data Access</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37787e1_d37788e1_d37789e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ypq1665702689055.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ypq1665702689055.html\" title=\"Specifies whether the component definition is cached in memory.\">Component Behavior</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37790e1_d37791e1_d37792e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cik1665702689127.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cik1665702689127.html\" title=\"Sets the value of the &lt;$cmpStatemanagedBy&gt; constant, which specifies the mechanism used to save state information for the component.\">State Managed By</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37793e1_d37794e1_d37795e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xhw1665702689197.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xhw1665702689197.html\" title=\"Determines whether the component can run on a server without reference to global objects or a user interface. Valid values are T or F (default).\">Self-Contained</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__p_d95423e1_d95424e1_d95425e1\">Data I/O Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__ul_osd_3fn_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37796e1_d37797e1_d37798e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iku1665702689266.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iku1665702689266.html\" title=\"Name of the Keyboard Translation Table used to interpret field data upon input.\">Input Translation</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37799e1_d37800e1_d37801e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dbe1665702689335.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dbe1665702689335.html\" title=\"Name of the Keyboard Translation Table used to convert field data upon output.\">Output Translation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__p_d95426e1_d95427e1_d95428e1\">Presentation Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__ul_ssd_3fn_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37802e1_d37803e1_d37804e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"myt1665702689407.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/myt1665702689407.html\" title=\"Title displayed in the window title bar or browser tab when the application shell, form, or server page is run. If no title is specified, the object name is displayed.\">Title</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__p_d95429e1_d95430e1_d95431e1\">Character Mode Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__ul_vsd_3fn_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37805e1_d37806e1_d37807e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fel1665702689477.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fel1665702689477.html\" title=\"Number of header lines displayed at the top of the component in character mode. The remainder of the form is scrolled. No default.\">Header Length</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37808e1_d37809e1_d37810e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lma1665702689548.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lma1665702689548.html\" title=\"Determines whether the screen is cleared before and after running a form that runs another form. Applicable only when the form is run in character mode. True or False (Default).\">Clear?</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37811e1_d37812e1_d37813e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rmo1665702689618.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rmo1665702689618.html\" title=\"Determines whether a rectangular border is displayed around the form component's outer edge in character mode.\">Borderline</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37814e1_d37815e1_d37816e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ngp1665702689690.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ngp1665702689690.html\" title=\"Display the field in reversed highlighting. Applicable only to Unifields.\">Inverse</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37817e1_d37818e1_d37819e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"abx1665702689822.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/abx1665702689822.html\" title=\"Display the field as bold. Applicable only to Unifields.\">Bright</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37820e1_d37821e1_d37822e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lhp1665702689890.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lhp1665702689890.html\" title=\"Display the field as underlined. Applicable only to Unifields.\">Underline</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37823e1_d37824e1_d37825e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"avq1665702689959.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/avq1665702689959.html\" title=\"Apply blinking to the field. Applicable only to Unifields.\">Blink</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__section_shw_pfn_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d181960e594\">Triggers</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__ul_cqk_rfn_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37826e1_d37827e1_d37828e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kez1665702582531.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kez1665702582531.html\" title=\"Handles processing when an Accept request is received, usually with the intention of closing the component and keeping all changes made on it. This trigger is exposed as an operation in the component signature.\">trigger accept</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37829e1_d37830e1_d37831e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aag1665703130023.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aag1665703130023.html\" title=\"Trigger that reacts to the user's request to start over with a clean form.\">trigger clear</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37832e1_d37833e1_d37834e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"two1665703130263.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/two1665703130263.html\" title=\"Trigger that deletes all occurrences currently in the component, both in the external structure, and in the database. This is a very dangerous trigger—use it with extreme care!\">trigger erase</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37835e1_d37836e1_d37837e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jzq1665702665465.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jzq1665702665465.html\" title=\"Interactive trigger that responds to the form getting focus.\">trigger getFocus (Form)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37838e1_d37839e1_d37840e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oxi1665702665543.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oxi1665702665543.html\" title=\"ProcScript module that responds to the form losing focus. It can be used to verify the data to ensure that it is complete or correct.\">trigger loseFocus (Form)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37841e1_d37842e1_d37843e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xye1665702608643.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xye1665702608643.html\" title=\"Trigger that responds to a request for a menu in a desktop application.\">trigger menu</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37844e1_d37845e1_d37846e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hmh1665703130535.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hmh1665703130535.html\" title=\"Location for ProcScript that retrieves data from the database.\">trigger retrieve</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37847e1_d37848e1_d37849e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jno1665702661208.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jno1665702661208.html\" title=\"Trigger that retrieves the next occurrence in the database with a primary key value greater than the current one.\">trigger retrieveSequential</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37850e1_d37851e1_d37852e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hmn1665702683413.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hmn1665702683413.html\" title=\"System trigger that provides component-specific post-processing.\">trigger postActivate</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37853e1_d37854e1_d37855e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"muo1665702683268.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/muo1665702683268.html\" title=\"System trigger that provides component-specific pre-processing. It is required in web applications to recreate the component state.\">trigger preActivate</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37856e1_d37857e1_d37858e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ita1665703130455.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ita1665703130455.html\" title=\"Interactive trigger for responding to a print request.\">trigger print</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37859e1_d37860e1_d37861e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sux1665703129629.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sux1665703129629.html\" title=\"Interactive trigger for responding to a request for a pulldown menu in a desktop application.\">trigger pullDown</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37862e1_d37863e1_d37864e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ghq1665702608876.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ghq1665702608876.html\" title=\"Reacts to asynchronous messages that come from outside the application.\">trigger receiveMessage</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37865e1_d37866e1_d37867e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jvb1665703130778.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jvb1665703130778.html\" title=\"Trigger that responds to a request to save (store) the data.\">trigger store</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37868e1_d37869e1_d37870e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qun1665702582075.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qun1665702582075.html\" title=\"Trigger that handles processing when a Quit request is received, usually with the intention of closing the component without saving any modifications made in it. This trigger is exposed as an operation in the component signature.\">trigger quit</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vfj1665703025321__li_d37871e1_d37872e1_d37873e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"niy1665702606431.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/niy1665702606431.html\" title=\"Trigger for responding to user-defined key sequences as defined in the Keyboard Translation Table (KTT) or defined in the usys.ini section named as userkeys.\">trigger userKey</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616489\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616489\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Modeled Component Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Modeled Component A Modeled Component is a Component that can be used to create derived components, which inherit the component-level properties, code containers, and constants from the modeled component. Modeled components are used to speed development and ensure consistency between components with a similar purpose. A modeled component defines a pattern for a specific type of component, including its structure, properties, and layout, and this pattern is copied to components that are derived from it. Characteristics Characteristics Object type code: cpt Main Development Object? Yes Part of: — Contains: Component Entity , Label , Property , Code Container , Generic Entity, Generic Field Generalization: Main Development Object Specializations — Compilation Output — Example URI: cpt: ModeledComponentName Specialization Modeled Component specializes Main Development Object and Component in the following ways: The Modeled Component property is True . This causes Uniface to automatically define compile-time constants for any generic entities and fields. It can contain generic entities and fields. No runtime objects are generated. Properties Object Properties: Name Type Location Description Documentation Source Properties: Date Modified Configuration Properties: Library Is Modeled Component Modeled Component Behavior Properties: Component Type Data Access Component Behavior State Managed By Self-Contained Data I/O Properties: Input Translation Output Translation Presentation Properties: Title Character Mode Properties: Header Length Clear? Borderline Inverse Bright Underline Blink Triggers trigger accept trigger clear trigger erase trigger getFocus (Form) trigger loseFocus (Form) trigger menu trigger retrieve trigger retrieveSequential trigger postActivate trigger preActivate trigger print trigger pullDown trigger receiveMessage trigger store trigger quit trigger userKey Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}